<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c1">" إبراهيم بن يزيد النحوي"</span>:<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c5">أول من سمعت منه:</span> <span class="c2">(ما عداهما)</span> .<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
